
* Ways to resolve
	- In *.xinitrc* add *xrandr --auto*. This will automatically set up the display outputs.
	- In */etc/X11/xorg.conf* add:
	  @code
			Section "ServerFlags"
				Option "BlankTime" "0"
				Option "StandbyTime" "0"
				Option "SuspendTime" "0"
				Option "OffTime" "0"
				Option "DPMS" "false"
			EndSection
		@end

